# GlobalMedCare – Requirements Document

## 1. Functional Requirements

- AI-based Symptom Checker
- Risk Score Generation
- Emergency One-Tap Button
- Live Ambulance Tracking
- Nearest Hospital Finder
- Blood Availability Information
- Verified Doctor Video Consultation
- Digital Health Records (ABHA integration)
- Medicine Availability Tracker
- Mental Health Support
- Government Scheme Mapping

## 2. Non-Functional Requirements

- Low-latency response (<3 seconds)
- Secure Cloud Storage
- Role-based Access Control
- Regional Language Support
- Scalable AWS Infrastructure
- Data Privacy Compliance

## 3. Target Users

- Rural & Urban Citizens
- Hospitals
- Doctors
- Government Health Agencies# GlobalMedCare – System Design

## 1. Architecture Overview

User App (Mobile/Web)
        ↓
API Gateway
        ↓
Backend Services (AWS Cloud)
        ↓
Database (Secure Health Records)
        ↓
AI Engine (Symptom Analysis & Risk Scoring)

## 2. Core Modules

- Emergency Management Module
- AI Symptom Checker Module
- Telemedicine Module
- Hospital & Ambulance Integration Module
- Medicine & Blood Availability Module
- Digital Health Record System
- Government Scheme Mapping Engine

## 3. Security Design

- End-to-End Encryption
- OAuth 2.0 Authentication
- Role-Based Access Control
- Secure Cloud Storage (AWS Compatible)

## 4. Scalability Plan

- Microservices Architecture
- Auto Scaling on Cloud
- Load Balancer Integration
- API-based External Integration
